{"path": "/data6/user24215463/Wan2.2/Wan2.2_SA3_fullrepo_fp16_edges_sagetriton_v0/README_ROWMAX_TRANSFER.md", "kind": "file", "size": 886, "mtime": 1781244573, "head": "# Wan2.2 Row-Max Calibration Transfer Bundle\n\nThis bundle contains only row-max calibration code and prompt files. It does not contain model weights, generated videos, profiles, or caches.\n\n## Install\n\nExtract at the destination `Wan2.2_zdh` root, where weights already exist:\n\n```bash\ncd /path/to/Wan2.2_zdh\ntar -xzf /path/to/rowmax_calibration_code_bundle_20260608.tar.gz\n```\n\n## Run\n\n```bash\nbash collect_rowmax_fp16.sh\n```\n\nDefaults: `CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=0`, `t2v-A14B`, `VIDEO_SIZE=480*832`, fp16 row-level row max, 1024x1024 blocks, one profile file per prompt, cond/uncond separated, video save/decode skipped.\n\nSmoke test one prompt and one sampling step:\n\n```bash\nLIMIT=1 SAMPLE_STEPS=1 bash collect_rowmax_fp16.sh\n```\n\nIf paths differ:\n\n```bash\nZDH_ROOT=/path/to/Wan2.2_zdh WAN_CODE_DIR=/path/to/Wan2.2_zdh/Wan2.2 CKPT_DIR=/path/to/Wan2.2_zdh bash collect_rowmax_fp16.sh\n```\n"}
