{"path": "/data6/user24215463/Wan2.2/Wan2.2_SA3_fullrepo_fp16_edges_sagetriton_v0/README_ROWMAX_FULL_CODE_TRANSFER.md", "kind": "file", "size": 971, "mtime": 1781244573, "head": "# Wan2.2 Row-Max Full Code Transfer Bundle\n\nThis archive contains the full `Wan2.2/` source tree with row-max calibration changes, plus the calibration prompt files and `collect_rowmax_fp16.sh` inside `Wan2.2/`.\n\nIt excludes model weights, generated videos, images, row-max profiles, caches, and git metadata.\n\n## Extract\n\nExtract from the parent directory where you want `Wan2.2/` to live:\n\n```bash\ncd /root\ntar -xzf /path/to/Wan2.2_rowmax_full_code_bundle_20260608.tar.gz\n```\n\n## Smoke Test\n\nUse your real checkpoint path:\n\n```bash\ncd /root/Wan2.2\nCKPT_DIR=/root/autodl-tmp/Wan2.2-T2V-A14B LIMIT=1 SAMPLE_STEPS=1 bash collect_rowmax_fp16.sh\n```\n\n## Full Calibration\n\n```bash\ncd /root/Wan2.2\nCKPT_DIR=/root/autodl-tmp/Wan2.2-T2V-A14B bash collect_rowmax_fp16.sh\n```\n\nDefaults: CUDA device 0, `t2v-A14B`, `480*832`, fp16 row-level row max, 1024x1024 blocks, one profile file per prompt, cond/uncond separated, T5 on CPU, model offload enabled, video decode/save skipped.\n"}
